{"abstract": "Seventeen employees of the American oil giant Chevron and the rig operator Transocean could face charges connected to an offshore oil spill, adding to Chevron\u2019s woes in Brazil.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/19/business/energy-environment/brazil-bars-17-at-chevron-and-transocean-from-leaving-after-spill.html", "snippet": "Seventeen employees of the American oil giant Chevron and the rig operator Transocean could face charges connected to an offshore oil spill, adding to Chevron\u2019s woes in Brazil.", "lead_paragraph": "RIO DE JANEIRO \u2014 A Brazilian court has ordered 17 employees from two American companies, the oil giant Chevron and the rig operator Transocean, to surrender their passports, barring them from leaving Brazil as authorities prepare to file criminal charges in days in connection with an offshore oil spill involving the companies. ", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "9", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/03/19/business/spill-1/spill-1-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 389, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2012/03/19/business/spill-1/spill-1-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 389}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/03/19/business/spill-1/spill-1-jumbo.jpg", "height": 696, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2012/03/19/business/spill-1/spill-1-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2012/03/19/business/spill-1/spill-1-thumbStandard.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}], "headline": {"main": "Brazil Bars Oil Workers Fro